channel.title: Some Stuff In Client 448
channel.description:
Heres some things I found, whether or not they help at all, you decide. I'm currently working on making the client connect to private servers.
Class16 - aClass71_426 = Class53_Sub14_Sub6.method697("headicons_prayer", -46); class53_Sub14_Sub12_Sub5 - aClass71_3335 = Class53_Sub14_Sub6.method697("headicons_hint", -46); Class63 - aClass71_1488 = Class53_Sub14_Sub6.method697("headicons_pk", -46); Class9 - Connecting to update server Class16 - Welcome to RuneScape Class17 - This is whats stopping us from connecting to the german servers if you were no invited. Class23 - Directs it to where the cache is on your computer Class29 - has an ::errortest command Class34 - Unexpected server response is found in here Class35 - Loaded sprites, So theres are pictures in the cache? Class38 - Account locked as we suspect it has been stolen Class39 - This computers address has been blocked Class41 - more sprite loading? Class42 - Jagex has a ::noclip command? lol Class51 - They even have a ::clientdrop? Class53_Sub9 - Unexpected loginserver response Class53_Sub10 - "Password: " might help for adding an IP: Class53_Sub10_Sub1 aClass71_2327 = Class53_Sub14_Sub6.method697("::", -46); the base for client commands? (Forgot what class it was in lol) Class53_Sub12 - Your account has been disabled
If any of this helps post lol...
